{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"APPROACH A\n      \n        website/ (existing Astro starter)\n        ├── restyle global.css → serif + red accent\n        ├── rewrite index.astro → your homepage\n        ├── add remark-math + rehype-katex\n        ├── replace header icons → LinkedIn/X/email\n        └── delete sample blog posts, add yours\n        Builds on what's already there\n      \n    \n    \n      A — Restyle the starter (recommended)\n      Keep the Astro blog starter as-is, restyle it to match Literary Minimal, add LaTeX. Fastest path. The starter already has MDX, content collections, RSS, and a solid blog layout. No reason to rebuild what works.\n      \n        ProsDone fastestProven blog infrastructureEasy to maintain\n        ConsInherits some starter opinions on structure","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1776201691415}
